parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the windshield wipers can reduce visibility while driving, especially in rainy or snowy conditions, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The windshield wipers work periodically
the windshield wipers stop and won't restart
the windshield wipers turn off while driving
the windshield wipers come back on and then turn off again.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of rear brake lines can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can result in accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
poor braking
brake fluid leakage
stream of fluid coming out of the steel line.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) can cause a loss of braking ability, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Pulsing of the brake pedal
loss of braking ability
ABS activation without proper braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of fuel lines can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires or other safety hazards.
symptoms: Fuel line corrosion
fuel leaks
custom fuel lines needed.

the airbag system may not function properly in the event of a crash
the vehicle may not pass safety inspections.
